⍝ EachDyadic.tc
⍝ ═════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO dyadic function; A and B conformable
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ ⍴B (when ⍴A≡⍴B)
      ⍝ inv: I⊃Z ←→ (I⊃A) LO I⊃B
      ⍝ inv: A LO¨ B ←→ A LO B  (when both scalars)
      A ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← A +¨ B
      (⍴Z) ≡ ⍴B
1
      ⍝ Element-wise: I⊃Z ←→ (I⊃A)+(I⊃B)
      Z ≡ A + B
1
      ⍝ Scalar each: A LO¨ B ←→ A LO B
      A ← ⎕RVAL 0
      B ← ⎕RVAL 0
      (A +¨ B) ≡ A + B
1
